This is a non-DOCSIS cable modem. :Specifically, it uses '''Motorola''''s proprietary CDLP system. :See {{WPLink|Cable modem#CDLP}} for a bit more info.
Early '''@Home Network''' installations may have been the principal :users of these modems.. though some post '''@Home''' networks :may have kept the legacy network going for a bit longer.
